'''''Birkby''''' was the group designation for a force of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]]. They assisted the [[Independence/Legends|''Independence'']] that hosted the diplomatic meeting with the [[Habassa]], during which they were attacked by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigates]] ''[[Havok]]'' and ''[[Riptide]]''.

